Package police

A client for the UK Police Data API.

Package police Description

A client for the UK Police Data API.

See the API documentation

The Police Data API allows its users to access crime data. It is a RESTful service, and uses JSON to return data. Therefore, this code uses either the com.google.gson.JsonParser low-level classes, or the com.google.gson.Gson reflection-based parser depending on where it makes sense.
